                     <interp inst="t18120916-98-person817" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I received this horse-hair of Mr. Wells, and I took the prisoner in custody.</p>
               <p>MR. WELLS. I believe it is our property.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I never was guilty of a criminal action in my life.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called one witness, who gave him a good character.</p>
